---
---
<section class="location section section-warm" id="contacto">
  <div class="container">
    <span class="loc-eyebrow">Enc&uacute;entranos</span>
    <h2 class="section-title">Nuestra Ubicaci&oacute;n</h2>
    <div class="gold-divider"></div>

    <div class="loc-grid">
      <div class="loc-map">
        <div class="map-placeholder">
          <div class="map-pin">&#128205;</div>
          <div class="map-address">
            <strong>Fuego & Saz&oacute;n</strong><br/>
            Av. La Mar 1290, Miraflores
          </div>
          <div class="map-overlay-text">
            <a href="https://maps.google.com/?q=Av.+La+Mar+1290+Miraflores+Lima" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm">
              Abrir en Google Maps
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="loc-info">
        <div class="loc-card">
          <div class="loc-icon">&#127968;</div>
          <div>
            <h4>Direcci&oacute;n</h4>
            <p>Av. La Mar 1290<br/>Miraflores, Lima 15074<br/>Per&uacute;</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="loc-card">
          <div class="loc-icon">&#128222;</div>
          <div>
            <h4>Contacto</h4>
            <p>Tel: (01) 445-8899<br/>WhatsApp: +51 987 654 321<br/>Email: hola@fuegoyazon.pe</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="loc-card">
          <div class="loc-icon">&#128663;</div>
          <div>
            <h4>Estacionamiento</h4>
            <p>Estacionamiento gratuito para clientes en la parte trasera del local (10 espacios). Tambi&eacute;n hay parqueo p&uacute;blico en la cuadra.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="loc-card">
          <div class="loc-icon">&#128652;</div>
          <div>
            <h4>C&oacute;mo llegar</h4>
            <p>A 5 minutos del Parque Kennedy. Referencia: cruce de Av. La Mar con Calle Berlín. Accesible en Metropolitano (Estaci&oacute;n Benavides).</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .loc-eyebrow {
    display: block;
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--gold);
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .loc-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
    align-items: start;
  }
  .map-placeholder {
    width: 100%;
    height: 420px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e8d5b7, #c9b896);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
  }
  .map-placeholder::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background:
      linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.1) 1px, transparent 1px),
      linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.1) 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 40px 40px;
  }
  .map-pin {
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    animation: float 3s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  @keyframes float {
    0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
    50% { transform: translateY(-10px); }
  }
  .map-address {
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--primary);
    font-size: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .btn-sm { padding: 0.6rem 1.5rem; font-size: 0.85rem; }
  .loc-info {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }
  .loc-card {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: 1.25rem;
    background: white;
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }
  .loc-card:hover {
    transform: translateX(4px);
  }
  .loc-icon {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: var(--warm);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
  }
  .loc-card h4 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--primary);
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }
  .loc-card p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--text-light);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .loc-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .map-placeholder { height: 300px; }
  }
</style>
